## ⚙️ Configuration

The app saves your business details in `config.json` for future use.

For email functionality, you need a Gmail App Password:
- Enable 2-Factor Authentication in Gmail
- Generate App Password at: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
- Add credentials to `config.json`

